; Coverage test for xact.cc lines 1119-1133
; Tests auto-xact cost derivation when the initial post has a cost
; and the auto-generated amount has a price annotation (from @@).
; The auto-xact copies the amount and derives cost from the annotation.
; This exercises the ANNOTATION_PRICE_NOT_PER_UNIT + negative sign path.

= Expenses:Energy
    Liabilities:Tax  (amount)
    Assets:Tax       (-amount)

2024/03/01 Electric Bill
    Expenses:Energy       100 kWh @@ 72 EUR
    Assets:Checking

test reg --generated
24-Mar-01 Electric Bill         Expenses:Energy             100 kWh      100 kWh
                                Assets:Checking              EUR-72       EUR-72
                                                                         100 kWh
                                Liabilities:Tax             100 kWh       EUR-72
                                                                         200 kWh
                                Assets:Tax                 -100 kWh       EUR-72
                                                                         100 kWh
end test
